history.content: Post on Data 001, the advisors there will be the ones who can help

<md>I got an approved petition to replace Data 8 with Stat 20 for the purposes of enrolling in Data 100 for my data science minor.

> Your petition to substitute Stat 20 in Summer 2021 or Fall 2021 for the Data 8 requirement in the Data Science minor is approved, assuming that you complete the course with a minimum letter grade of C- or better (a Pass is acceptable in Summer 2021) and you also complete CS 61A or 88 toward the minor.

I am currently taking Stat 20, but can't phase 1 Data 100 due to lack of prerequisites. Who do I contact to be enrolled in the class?</md>
history.subject: Approved Petition to Substitute Stat 20 for Data 8 - How to enroll in Data 100?
